```
push -- add to end
pop -- remove from end
back, back!, back? -- get from end
take -- take first i elms
drop -- drop first i elms
modify -- change elm at given i
eraseIdx -- erase elm at i
zipIdx -- enumerate, i.e. zip with range
range' -- range but with start/stop
replicate -- fill an array with a given value; repeat an identical value; repeat the same value

Array.getInternal is used with notation: xarray[i]
Array.get!Internal is used with notation: xarray[i]!
